GENERAL INFOS

#This is a standard comment
to comment a whole line press 
# Strg + #
to run press 
# Strg + F5 
to create a python file you have to name it "file.py"
to open the terminal you have to press Strg + Shift + P  -> Create Terminal  or 
# Strg + Shift + รถ

VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENT

each folder/project should have an virtual environment (Workspace)
to create an env type in the terminal: 
# py -3 -m venv nameofthevirtualenvironment

activate an envorinment in terminal: 
# nameofthevirtualenvironment\Scripts\activate
wichtig  powershell scripts zulassen: https://www.anreiter.at/ausfuehrung-von-powershell-scripts-zulassen/

INSTALL PACKAGES

install packages in an new venv:
# py -m pip install "packagename"
or
# pip install packagename

requirements file:
create an requirements.txt file (with the installed packages of the venv) 
# pip freeze > requirements.txt
install packages from requirements.txt
# pip install -r requirements.txt

